PrecisAuthority for the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an Agreement with ONTARIO to amend the provincial annex to the AGRICULTURAL INCOME DISASTER ASSISTANCE PROGRAM AGREEMENT to allow the Province to include Status Indians as eligible applicants for its share of program payments.

precis:
Authority for the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into
an Agreement with ONTARIO to amend the provincial annex to the AGRICULTURAL
INCOME DISASTER ASSISTANCE PROGRAM AGREEMENT to allow the Province to
include Status Indians as eligible applicants for its share of program
payments.
